BR/EDR generic packet structure (PAGE 210)
  Channel Access Code | Packet Header | Guard & Sync(EDR Only) | Payload Header | Payload Body | MIC | CRC
  
LE generic packet structure (page 211)
  LE radio operation is based on three PHYs (LE 1M. 2M, LE Coded) and makes use of two modulation schemes (1 Msym/s, 2 Msym/s modulation).
  
  
  
  
